    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n3717" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐργάζομαι</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ϝέργον</span>), ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">εἰργάζετο, ἐργάζοντο</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">work, do, perform;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κέλευσε δε ϝεργάζεσθαι</span>, bade his
          bellows <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">be at work</span>, <i><span class="en">Il.
            18.469</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; ἔργα ἐργάζεσθαι,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Od. 20.72</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">
            ἐναίσιμα</span>, ‘do what is right,’ <i><span class="en">Od. 17.321</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; χρῡσὸν εἰργ&lt;&gt;ζετο</span>,
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">wrought</span>, <i><span class="en">Od.
          3.435</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
